{"tid":1460443,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"總括今日林鄭記者會表現","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:36:24.000Z","uid":26619,"like":960,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"70c41e7c2d8e5bd20da605d121b2618ad0dcf0f2","tid":1460443,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"1. 30分鐘的記者，遲到6分鐘 。 先減2分<br />\n2. 想喊無喊唔出，交唔到戲。再減兩分<br />\n3. 粉身碎骨，咁重要的詞語，應用行動表達，如撕爛講稿，浪費機會。減3分<br />\n4. 回答外媒，竟然唔跟華春瑩講：我國內政，豈容你說三道四。減2分。<br />\n5. 全情死狗唔耐煩的樣子。減1分 <br />\n<br />\n但最後提早結束，無謂浪費大家時間。加10分。<br />\n<br />\n所以林鄭今日表現係滿分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b131aff20f6589744dae042cdda42c8ae038d5","tid":1460443,"uid":13187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e32e17115a6dea2dc4141449e5ec250eedcd14","tid":1460443,"uid":41524,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"不錯分析"},{"pid":"ae904d69edda51d91fae1f87d5713a177f314002","tid":1460443,"uid":263298,"like":255,"dislike":14,"score":241,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"一見到佢個樣已經想扣佢50分"},{"pid":"78ed286ad0dbbb9a1377c43d0f8289ce9aafd08f","tid":1460443,"uid":26619,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"75e32e17115a6dea2dc4141449e5ec250eedcd14","tid":1460443,"uid":41524,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"不錯分析"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"我一向持平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03603a99100188637bfcbd83655e6bd545d27b4e","tid":1460443,"uid":35580,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"ae904d69edda51d91fae1f87d5713a177f314002","tid":1460443,"uid":263298,"like":255,"dislike":14,"score":241,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"一見到佢個樣已經想扣佢50分"},"citedBy":0,"reply